quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  39,1,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  39,2,"Men jippiniirii Deftere nden e maa…óa, e hoore goonga. rewu Allah, la…ì…ìinanaa Mo diina kan"
  39,3,"Anndee, ko Allah woodani diina laa…ìuka kan. ∆Åen non …ìe …ìeya jogitori yi…ó…ìe gaanin Makko (hara hi…ìe wi'a): \"Men alaa rewirde …ói, si wanaa tun no …ói …ìannira men ka Allah, …ìadal\". Pellet, Allah √±aawoyay hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, e kon ko …ìe woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah fewnataa on won…óo fewnoowo, …óuu…óu…óo yeddugol"
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yi…óuno, nde O siforta …ìi…ó…óo, O su…ìayno ko O yi…ói woo, e ko O tagi kon. Senayee woodanii Mo ! Ko Kanko woni Allah, Bajjo, Foolu…óo On"
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, goonga.Himo suddira jemma on √±alorma on, O suddira √±alorma on jemma on. O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal. Anndee, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, Haforoowo On"
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi O wa…ói e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraa…ói …óin, nooneeji jeetati. Himo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu …ìaawo tagu, e nder ni…ìe tati. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko Kanko laamu woodani. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Allah. Ko honno ferlitora…óon [e rewugol Mo]"
  39,7,"Si on yeddii, anndon Allah, ko yondinii…óo e mon. O ja…ìantaa jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, keeferaaku. Si on yettii Mo non, O weltanoo on …óum.Hay gooto roondantaako go…ó…óo woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollayno…óon. Pellet, ko O anndu…óo, ko woni e …ìer…óe"
  39,8,"Si loraa memii ne…ó…óo on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e Makko. Refti si O okkii mo mo∆¥∆¥ere, immorde ka Makko, o yejjita ko o noddaynoo kon ado …óum, o wa…óana Allah kafidii…ói, fii no o majjinira (yim…ìe …ìen) e laawol Makko ngol. MaAku: \"Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, see…óa. Pellet, ko a jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Yiite …ìen"
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotoo…óo tummbo jemma, ko o sujjoowo, darotoo…óo (naafe), hara himo laakara, himo jortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: \"Hara anndu…ìe …ìen fotay e …ìe anndaa …ìen?\" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,10,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe, hulee Joomi mon\". Hino woodani mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe (golle) …ìen e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Anndee mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen timminirante njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko aldaa e limoore"
  39,11,"Maaku: \"Min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah, la…ì…ìinana Mo diina kan"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, wonugol arano e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  39,13,"Maaku : \"Min mi…óo huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √ëalaande Mawnde"
  39,14,"Maaku: \"Ko Allah mi rewata, mi la…ì…ìinan Mo diina am"
  39,15,"rewee ko yi…óu…óon onon, hara wanaa Kanko. Maaku: \"Ko woni hayru…ìe …ìen, ko …ìen …ìe tawata √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe hayrinii ko'e ma…ì…ìe, e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe\". Anndee ko nden woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
  39,16,"Hino woodirani …ìe senngo dow ma…ì…ìe, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley ma…ì…ìe. Ko …óum woni ko Allah hul…ìinirta jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am, kori hulee Lam"
  39,17,"∆Åen wo…ó…óitor…ìe rewugol bewnooji …ói, …ìe ruttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani …ìe. Wewlinir jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen"
  39,18,"nanoo…ìe Konngol …ìen, …ìe jokka ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e maggol. Ko …ìen woni …ìe Allah fewni …ìen, ko …ìen woni joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,19,E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mun... E ko an da…óndata won…óo ka Yiite
  39,20,"Si ko …ìen hulu…ìe Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìe ku…ìeeje [ka Aljanna] e ku…ìeeje mahaa…óe dow majje, hara can…ói no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore. @Corrected"
  39,21,"E a yi'aali, wonnde Allah saa∆¥inirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi …óam e nder …ìulli ka leydi; refti O yaltinira …óam remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu …óay…óa, yi'aa hindu soy…ói; refti O wa…óa …óum ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e …óum, waaju, wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah ya√±√±ani …ìendre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii …ìen yooru…ìe …ìer…óe mun, e jantagol Allah. ∆Åen wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [√±aawooje], …óimmitunde. Nde guri …ìen huloo…ìe Joomi mun ri…ìirta (nanugol nde), refti guri e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe dee∆¥ira jantoore Allah nden. Ko …óum woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentarii…óo yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bon…óe …óen √ëalnde Darngal... Too√±u…ìe …ìen wi'anee ontuma: \"Mee…óee kon ko wonuno…óon faggitanaade"
  39,25,"Adinoo…ìe …ìen fenniino, lepte …óen ardirani …ìe, ka …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah mee…óiniri …ìe koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara …óen non, …ìuri mawnude, si tawno hi…ìe anndunoo"
  39,27,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, …ìe waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e oo√±aare, fii no …ìe gom…óira"
  39,29,"Allah wa…óii misal, gorko mo lurru…ìe hawti …óum, hi…ìe poo…óondira mo, e gorko laa…ìan…óo gorko [goo]: Hara …ìen …ói…óo fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kam…ìe kadi ko …ìe maayoo…ìe"
  39,31,"refti onon, √ëalnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"
  39,32,"E ko hommbo …ìuri too√±de wa on fenu…óo e hoore Allah, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,33,"On non ardu…óo e goonga, o goongini …óum, ko …ìen woni gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko …ìe faaletee, ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe; ko …óum njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  39,35,"fii no Allah yawtirana …ìe, ko …ìuri bonnde e ko …ìe golli kon, O yo…ìitira …ìe njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaa…óo Makko on? Hi…ìe hul…ìinire …óin …ói wonaa Mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah fewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali wonnde Foolu…óo, Jom lepte"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a lamndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin?\", ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Allah\". Maaku: \"Yeetee lam fii …óin …ói rewoton gaanin Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara …ói huncanay lam lorra Makko kan? Maa si O faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si …ói ha…óay lam yurmeende Makko nden? Maaku: \"Allah yonii lam, ko e Makko hoolnotoo…ìe …ìen tuuginotoo"
  39,39,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, gollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi gollirta. Aray ka anndon"
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte hoynay…óe aroyat e muu…óum, lepte duumii…óe jippoo e makko"
  39,41,"Men jippinirii Deftere nden e maa…óa, fii yim…ìe …ìen, e hoore goonga. Kala feewu…óo, ko hoore makko [o feewani]; kala kadi majju…óo, ko hoore makko o majjani. A wonaali wakiil e dow ma…ì…ìe"
  39,42,"Allah hino ∆¥ettita pittaali …óin, saanga maayde majji, e …óin …ói maayaali, ka …óoyngol majji. O jogitoo …óin …ói √±aawani maayde, O accita …óiya, haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal. Pellet, maandeeji woni e …óum, wonannde yim…ìe miijitotoo…ìe"
  39,43,"Kaa …ìe jogiti tefooji, gaanin Allah? Maaku: \"Hay si tawii …ói jeyaa huunde, …ói haqqiltaa kadi"
  39,44,"Maaku: \"Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Ko Kanko woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Refti ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jantaama, …ìer…ìe …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa laakara …ìen, tamoo. Si fii …óiya, …ói wonaa Mo [Kanko Allah] jantaama, e jaka yoo, hi…ìe wewla"
  39,46,"Maaku: \"Yaa Allah, Fu…ó…óu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Anndu…óo wirnii…ói e fee√±u…ói, ko An √±aawata hakkunde jeyaa…ìe Maa …ìen, kon ko …ìe luutondiraynoo e mun"
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodanno too√±u…ìe …ìen, ko woni kon ka leydi fow, e yeru mun, wonndude e mum, …ìe sottorayno …óum, bone lepte …óen, √ëalnde Darngal; fee√±irana …ìe ka Allah, kon ko …ìe tijjanooki"
  39,48,"boneeji …ói …ìe faggitinoo …óin fe√±ana …ìe, ko …ìe jalkitaynoo kon huu…ìita …ìe"
  39,49,"Si lorra he…ìii ne…ó…óo on, o nodda Men. Refti si Men okkii mo neema, immorde ka Amen, o wi'a: \"Anndee ko e ganndal [am] mi okkiira …óum\". ∆äum ko jarrabuyee kan; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  39,50,"Gom…óii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe wi'iino …óum. Kono kon ko …ìe faggitotonoo, nafaani …ìe"
  39,51,"boneeji …ói …ìe faggitotonoo …óin memi …ìe. Too√±u…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, kon ko …ìe wonunoo e faggitagol, memoyay …ìe, …ìe wonaali laawotoo…ìe"
  39,52,"E …ìe anndaa wonnde Allah no ya√±√±ana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ìillina [mo O muuyani]? Pellet, maandeeji wonii e …óum, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe"
  39,53,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am fantim…ìe e hoore mun, wata on ta∆¥o yurmeende Allah nden. Pellet, Allah ko haforoowo junubaajo …óin fow. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  39,54,"Tuubee rutto…óon ka Joomi mon, jebbilano…óon Mo, ado lepte …óen arde e mon, hara on faabetaake"
  39,55,"Jokkee ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko jippinaa e mon, immorde ka Joomi, ado lepte …óen ardude on, juhal, hara on so'aa anndude"
  39,56,"fii wata wonkii wi'oy: \"Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e fii Allah. Pellet, mi jeyano e …ìen jalkitoo…ìe"
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: \"Si Alah fewnuno lam, mi wonanyno jeyaa…óo e gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte …óen: \"Si feere ruttagol no woodannoo lam, mi jeyee e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  39,59,"Gasataa ! Tawde Aayeeje Am …óen aruno e maa…óa, fennu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,60,"√ëalnde Darngal, a yi'oya fennonoo…ìe e hoore Allah …ìen, hino …ìawli geece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,61,"Allah na da…óndira gom…óu…ìe …ìen, sabu maloore ma…ì…ìe nden. Bone memataa …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni sunoytoo…ìe"
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tagu…óo kala huunde, ko Kanko kadi woni Fawtii…óo kala huunde"
  39,63,"Ko Kanko sottir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin woodani. Yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Allah …ìen non, ko …ìen woni hayru…ìe(pertu…ìe) …ìen"
  39,64,"Maaku: \"E ko woori Allah, yamirton mi, yo mi rewu, onon …ìee majju…ìe"
  39,65,"Gom…óii wahayinaama e maa…óa, e …ìen adinoo…ìe ma: \"Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa …óen bonay jeye…óaa e hayru…ìe …ìen"
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, jeye…óaa e yettoo…ìe (Mo) …ìen"
  39,67,"∆Åe mawniniraali Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fow, ko tamannde Makko, √ëalnde Darngal, kammuuli …óin kadi taggiree √±aamo Makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkanta Mo"
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi kon fa…ó…óee, si wanaa …ìen …ìe Allah muuyani [da…óugol]. Refti wuttee e mayru …ói…óa…ìol, tawa ko …ìe darii…ìe habbitii"
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru ndun wallinee, Annabaa…ìe e seedee…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addee; goonga √±aawiree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, wanaa …ìe too√±etee…ìe"
  39,70,"wonki kala yo…ìee ko golli kon. Ko Kanko [Allah] …ìuri anndude ko …ìe gollata"
  39,71,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen soggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenu…ìe nge …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"E Nulaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo'on hewtaano on, janngaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Joomi mon, e moo…óon, …ìe rentina on hawrugol e ndee √±alaande mon?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,72,"[∆Åe] wi'anee: \"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen lutton ton. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,73,"Huloo…ìe Joomi mun …ìen kadi …óowitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenu…ìe mo …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon, on laa…ìii, naatiree mo, duumagol"
  39,74,"∆Åe wi'a ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinan…óo men fodoore Mun, O ronini men leydi [Aljanna] ndin, me…óen weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka men yi…ói\". Mbarjaari gollunoo…ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere …ìen mo∆¥∆¥ii"
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, hi…ìe taarii Arsi kin, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Goonga √±aawiree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Wi'ee ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tegeefo ngon"